latest_release.name: Version 2.0.2
latest_release.body:
- Update test matrix after WP 6.6 release [[#43](https://github.com/wp-cli/automated-tests/pull/43)]
- Run trunk tests only on PHP 7.2+ [[#41](https://github.com/wp-cli/automated-tests/pull/41)]
- Update GHA versions to fix node 20 worning [[#40](https://github.com/wp-cli/automated-tests/pull/40)]
- Update to WPCS v3 [[#38](https://github.com/wp-cli/automated-tests/pull/38)]
- Only test latest WP on PHP 7.0+ [[#37](https://github.com/wp-cli/automated-tests/pull/37)]
- Do not test WP trunk on PHP 5.6 [[#36](https://github.com/wp-cli/automated-tests/pull/36)]
- Update github actions versions [[#35](https://github.com/wp-cli/automated-tests/pull/35)]
- Add `dealerdirect/phpcodesniffer-composer-installer` to `composer.json` [[#34](https://github.com/wp-cli/automated-tests/pull/34)]
- Use ramsey/composer-install@v2 [[#33](https://github.com/wp-cli/automated-tests/pull/33)]
- Switch from Travis CI to GitHub Actions [[#32](https://github.com/wp-cli/automated-tests/pull/32)]
